# Lightweight fallback desktop (XFCE). KDE Plasma 6 / KWin can black-screen in
# some VMs (no GPU compositing); XFCE renders fine with plain software graphics,
# so the live ISO can always reach a usable desktop. KDE Plasma stays the
# primary desktop and is selectable at the login screen.
xfce4-session
xfwm4
xfce4-panel
xfdesktop4
xfce4-settings
xfce4-terminal
xfce4-appfinder
thunar
